    a Digimon card with the [Angel]/[Three Great Angels]\_trait among them with the
    digivolution cost reduced by 2. Then, shuffle your security stack. If this effect
    digivolved, you may place 1 Digimon card with the [Angel]/[Archangel]/[Three
    Great Angels]\_trait from the hand at the bottom of your security stack."
